iggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係起緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起到2046<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fb3d5573131b958b19eb69793b405b5b033155","tid":336053,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>珠海還珠海,澳門還澳門,大把錢快啲起</blockquote><br />\nagger</blockquote><br />\n岩呀 唔通福田站有 香港就唔起咩</blockquote><br />\n當年錦上路方案都嫌遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果澳門要起點計都要喺氹仔設站先算方便啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0071f991af2501d1c0b65c5ec66db90ead23497d","tid":336053,"uid":69614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:17:11.000Z","msg":"高鐵直入賭場, 賭場做埋一地兩檢, <br />\n唔出賭場就唔洗過關<br />\n以後去澳門嫖賭飲吹不留痕跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebcb12cb90ecd3c9343dfb23456a144c4f00a1bd","tid":336053,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:18:30.000Z","msg":"應該整條高鐵線由香港&lt;-&gt;澳門"},{"pid":"5a87a7974e7a7dd72cbf064845166792982ba82d","tid":336053,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T11:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該整條高鐵線由香港&lt;-&gt;澳門</blockquote><br />\n要經香港，即係貶低澳門人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該起返條廣珠澳高鐵，澳門人都要一地兩檢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2179a54e15f8a71d615ab8592a99021bad2d056","tid":336053,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T11:56:28.000Z","msg":"你岩喎 起多個故宮比人喇屌"},{"pid":"0afb2a01420c8830f8082d5ddf41a8218fc4f871","tid":336053,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:03:21.000Z","msg":"[serious] 廣珠城際鐵路行常速200km/h快線 <br />\n膠鐵有名你叫XRL係HSR嘅 link / connection, 本身唔係高鐵 <br />\n引入ChiNA高鐵就係膠鐵取代區域快線其中一個根本問題所在"},{"pid":"8d6eb382aef36c04511d6b65b5797d6706644104","tid":336053,"uid":44510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:06:26.000Z","msg":"澳門好慘，要被邊沿化啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa4edc9df0163dcd8b456fee0f28b571b69902e","tid":336053,"uid":80072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:14:26.000Z","msg":"香港起緊嘅, 澳門都要起, 點可以大細超?"},{"pid":"171670a7bf1104a533821b598d4da186673ecea4","tid":336053,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T16:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[serious] 廣珠城際鐵路行常速200km/h快線 <br />\n膠鐵有名你叫XRL係HSR嘅 link / connection, 本身唔係高鐵 <br />\n引入ChiNA高鐵就係膠鐵取代區域快線其中一個根本問題所在</blockquote><br />\n如果西鐵當初係起四線，係咪可以夠位做埋區域快線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79371f3bee3d74d1f2b5d0471294c53b1fa9061","tid":336053,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T18:13:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>[serious] 廣珠城際鐵路行常速200km/h快線 <br />\n膠鐵有名你叫XRL係HSR嘅 link / connection, 本身唔係高鐵 <br />\n引入ChiNA高鐵就係膠鐵取代區域快線其中一個根本問題所在</blockquote><br />\n如果西鐵當初係起四線，係咪可以夠位做埋區域快線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1. 區域快線有共用西鐵北環線 <br />\n2. 西鐵綫行唔到200km/h <br />\n3. 四線化/並列複線擴展唔到服務空間 (西線: 八鄉上村, 梨木樹石籬)<br />\n4. 市區段會冇位(呢個都係建議源由), <br />\n想整速達車種或者短期內容納直通車應該起多月台同待避線(荃灣西站假假地都有條側線)  <br />\n個人會想兩者美孚站-南昌站交匯, 西鐵綫改經西九龍走廊, 設旺角西站, 讓少站嘅九龍南環線一半路段畀區域快線; 噉避免咗區域快線西線深水埗至葵涌停站真空, 改善連接. 總站放西九站定紅磡站都得; 原區域快線九龍半島段空間讓返畀東鐵綫地下化/起新線 (當然原方案圍繞紅磡站位置設計有佢著數)"},{"pid":"28c76d151390e2c3fce7229e6b06c235299f156c","tid":336053,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5748703e6c76e67de91bab21e7f035f83f37db09","tid":336053,"uid":19004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:34:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>珠海還珠海,澳門還澳門,大把錢快啲起</blockquote><br />\nagger</blockquote><br />\n岩呀 唔通福田站有 香港就唔起咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"若果福田高鐵站以至相關地區能夠撥歸香港（當然實施埋一地兩檢啦），那麼九龍、香港島、新界都可以有一個高鐵站"}]}